OL,3,CNottingham Attack families mark three
OL,4,Cyear anniversary
OL,6,FIt's three years to the day since
OL,7,Fthree people were killed on the
OL,8,Fstreets of Nottingham by a man who had
OL,9,Fbeen diagnosed with paranoid
OL,10,Fschizophrenia.
OL,12,FValdo Calocane killed students Barnaby
OL,13,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,14,F19, and grandfather Ian Coates, 65,
OL,15,Fbefore trying to murder Wayne Birkett,
OL,16,FSharon Miller and Marcin Gawronski
OL,17,Fwith a van on June 13 2023, in
OL,18,FNottingham, leaving them seriously
OL,19,Finjured.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
