OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781521369
OL,3,CNottingham Attack families mark three
OL,4,Cyear anniversary
OL,6,FHe is currently detained indefinitely
OL,7,Fin a high-security hospital after
OL,8,Fprosecutors accepted his not guilty
OL,9,Fpleas to murder, at his sentencing at
OL,10,FNottingham Crown Court in January 2024.
OL,12,FToday, the families of Grace O'Malley-
OL,13,FKumar, Barnaby Webber and Ian Coates
OL,14,Fled tributes to their loved ones, and
OL,15,Frenewed their call for justice.
OL,17,FA 15 minute service was held at St
OL,18,FPaul's Catholic Church in Nottingham.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
