CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781521369
OL,3,CNottingham Attack families mark three
OL,4,Cyear anniversary
OL,6,FFamily and friends then walked to
OL,7,FIlkeston Road and laid flowers where
OL,8,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar and Barnaby
OL,9,FWebber were stabbed.
OL,11,FDr Sanjoy Kumar, Grace's father, told
OL,12,FITV Central: "It's always nice to be
OL,13,Fback in Nottingham because this is
OL,14,Fwhere Grace had the best year of her
OL,15,Flife, and she said so. So I feel very
OL,16,Fwarm towards the people of Nottingham
OL,17,Fand Nottingham University."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
