PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781521369
OL,3,CNottingham Attack families mark three
OL,4,Cyear anniversary
OL,6,FThe families have just finished
OL,7,Flistening to evidence in The
OL,8,FNottingham Inquiry, looking into the
OL,9,Flead-up and aftermath of the attacks.
OL,11,FThe Nottingham Inquiry started on the
OL,12,F23rd of February and, since then, has
OL,13,Fheard from 164 witnesses over 14 weeks.
OL,15,FWork is now beginning on the report
OL,16,Fahead of a further hearing for closing
OL,17,Fsubmissions on 8th and 9th September.
OL,19,FThe Chair is required to deliver
OL,20,Ffindings and recommendations by May
OL,21,F2027.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
