FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781521369
OL,3,CNottingham Attack families mark three
OL,4,Cyear anniversary
OL,6,FLee Coates, Ian Coates' son, said
OL,7,Fafter this weekend of remembrance, the
OL,8,Ffamilies will be back on Monday
OL,9,Fmorning fighting.
OL,11,FHe said: "We've just endured from
OL,12,FFebruary a very intense inquiry. So to
OL,13,Ffinish that and the anniversary day
OL,14,Fbeing just around the corner, it just
OL,15,Fgoes to show it's never-ending, it
OL,16,Fdoesn't stop for us."
OL,18,FHe added: "We'll take this weekend to
OL,19,Fremember and celebrate the lives of
OL,20,Fthe people that we've lost, but Monday
OL,21,Fmorning we'll be back fighting again."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
