PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1781521369
OL,3,CNottingham Attack families mark three
OL,4,Cyear anniversary
OL,6,FCouncil Leader of Nottingham City
OL,7,FCouncil, Cllr Neghat Khan, said: "The
OL,8,FCouncil will reflect on the lessons
OL,9,Fand recommendations from the Inquiry
OL,10,Fwhen they are published.
OL,12,F"Nottingham will never forget and our
OL,13,Fthoughts are with the families of Ian,
OL,14,FBarnaby and Grace and those who
OL,15,Fsuffered injuries on the tragic day in
OL,16,FJune 2023."
